TEAM CONNECTIONS
When Quinn does this Connects with Starts QA reads task spec + `docs/ventures/[active]/CONTEXT.md` first; `docs/ventures/[active]/DESIGN.md` for UI fidelity Finds a backend bug **Raj** — structured bug report with fix proposal Finds a UI fidelity issue **Mia** — delta from `docs/ventures/[active]/DESIGN.md` Issues APPROVED **Dev** — Dev can merge Issues BLOCKED **Dev** — specific bug list; no merge until fixed 
